                                    <p><a href="https://freepostcodelottery.com/files/2017/05/HPD.png"><img class="size-medium wp-image-26663 alignright" src="https://freepostcodelottery.com/files/2017/05/HPD-300x170.png" alt="" width="300" height="170" srcset="https://freepostcodelottery.com/files/2017/05/HPD-300x170.png 300w, https://freepostcodelottery.com/files/2017/05/HPD-200x113.png 200w, https://freepostcodelottery.com/files/2017/05/HPD-80x45.png 80w, https://freepostcodelottery.com/files/2017/05/HPD-320x180.png 320w, https://freepostcodelottery.com/files/2017/05/HPD.png 600w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></p>
                                    <p class="lead">We all love winning, whether we’re winning money because of our postcode or combination of emojis, or winning free food. Well, now there’s another way to win: with your birthday!</p>
                                    <p>On <a href="http://www.happybirthdates.com/?uid=895458&amp;m=freepostcodelottery" target="_blank">happybirthdates.com</a> you could win £100 every day.</p>
                                    <p>All you have to do is join for free and then check the site each day to see if your birthday and initials have been drawn in any of ten daily draws. If you&#8217;re a winner you can claim your prize of £100. It’s as simple as that, and like all of our daily draws, there’s no purchase required &#8211; it’s completely free!</p>
                                    <p>Here’s why we like this daily draw so much; you can increase your own prize pool by shopping with Amazon through the happybirthdates.com product search page! If your birthday is drawn and you claim your prize, you’ll also receive 100% cashback on any purchases you’ve made through the site.</p>
