                                        <h2><a href="https://freepostcodelottery.com/video-draw-connections/">Video Draw Feedback</a></h2>
                                        <div class="entry-meta"><time class="updated" datetime="2017-05-24T15:29:06+01:00">May 24, 2017</time> <span class="byline author vcard">By <a href="https://freepostcodelottery.com/author/lshroff/" rel="author" class="fn">Laura</a></spam> | <a href="https://freepostcodelottery.com/category/competition-2/" rel="category tag">Competitions</a>, <a href="https://freepostcodelottery.com/category/news/" rel="category tag">News</a>, <a href="https://freepostcodelottery.com/category/video-draw/" rel="category tag">Video Draw</a></div>

                                        <div class="entry">
                                            <div class="pull-right blog-image"></div>

                                            <p><a href="https://freepostcodelottery.com/video" target="_blank"><img class="size-medium wp-image-26610 alignright" src="https://freepostcodelottery.com/files/2017/05/luke-desc-300x210.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="210" srcset="https://freepostcodelottery.com/files/2017/05/luke-desc-300x210.jpg 300w, https://freepostcodelottery.com/files/2017/05/luke-desc-768x539.jpg 768w, https://freepostcodelottery.com/files/2017/05/luke-desc-1024x718.jpg 1024w, https://freepostcodelottery.com/files/2017/05/luke-desc-200x140.jpg 200w, https://freepostcodelottery.com/files/2017/05/luke-desc-80x56.jpg 80w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></p>
                                            <p class="lead">We were so pleased to hear some lovely feedback from one of the artists featured on our video draw recently, <a href="https://play.spotify.com/artist/41RGqF0I6xFG0GzQmLKDgb?play=true&amp;utm_source=open.spotify.com&amp;utm_medium=open" target="_blank">Luke De-Sciscio</a>.</p>
                                            <p>He says he made some fantastic connections from his video and song being broadcast to so many people, namely a strong connection with a terminally ill cancer sufferer who used Luke’s songs during her relaxation therapy, and who came out to see one of his gigs in Bath.</p>
                                            <p>We’re super proud to be able to use our platform to share music with people who may not have found it... <a href="https://freepostcodelottery.com/video-draw-connections/">Read more &raquo;</a></p>


